#: ../../functions.md:1
msgid "Function calls"
msgstr "调用函数"

#: ../../functions.md:3
msgid "Loading libraries"
msgstr "加载库"

#: ../../functions.md:5
msgid ""
"To declare functions, start by loading the shared library with "
"`koffi.load(filename)`."
msgstr ""
"要定义导入函数, 先通过`koffi.load(filename)`来加载动态链接库."

#: ../../functions.md:14
msgid ""
"This library will be automatically unloaded once all references to it are"
" gone (including all the functions that use it, as described below)."
msgstr ""
"这个库会在所有引用(包含所有使用它的函数, 如下所述)结束后被自动卸载"

#: ../../functions.md:16
msgid ""
"Starting with *Koffi 2.3.20*, you can explicitly unload a library by "
"calling `lib.unload()`. Any attempt to find or call a function from this "
"library after unloading it will crash."
msgstr ""
"从`Koffi 2.3.20`起, 你可以通过调用`lib.unload()`来显式卸载一个库. 凡是在卸载尝试之后去查找或调用其中的函数都会导致程序崩溃."

#: ../../functions.md:19
msgid ""
"On some platforms (such as with the [musl C library on "
"Linux](https://wiki.musl-libc.org/functional-differences-from-glibc.html"
"#Unloading-libraries)), shared libraries cannot be unloaded, so the "
"library will remain loaded and memory mapped after the call to "
"`lib.unload()`."
msgstr ""
"某些平台(例如[使用musl C库的linux](https://wiki.musl-libc.org/functional-differences-from-glibc.html"
"#Unloading-libraries)), 动态链接库无法被卸载, 因此在调用`lib.unload()`后库仍然会被保持加载且映射到内存中."

#: ../../functions.md:22
msgid "Function definitions"
msgstr "定义函数"

#: ../../functions.md:24
msgid "Definition syntax"
msgstr "定义格式"

#: ../../functions.md:26
msgid ""
"Use the object returned by `koffi.load()` to load C functions from the "
"library. To do so, you can use two syntaxes:"
msgstr ""
"使用`koffi.load()`返回的对象来从库中加载C函数. 你可以使用两种语法来实现:"

#: ../../functions.md:28
msgid "The classic syntax, inspired by node-ffi"
msgstr "经典语法, 灵感来自node-ffi"

#: ../../functions.md:29 ../../functions.md:42
msgid "C-like prototypes"
msgstr "C风格的原型"

#: ../../functions.md:31
msgid "Classic syntax"
msgstr "经典语法"

#: ../../functions.md:33
msgid ""
"To declare a function, you need to specify its non-mangled name, its "
"return type, and its parameters. Use an ellipsis as the last parameter "
"for variadic functions."
msgstr ""
"要声明一个函数, 你需要指定它未修饰的名称, 它的返回类型以及它的参数. 对于可变参数函数, 使用省略号作为最后一个参数."

#: ../../functions.md:40
msgid ""
"Koffi automatically tries mangled names for non-standard x86 calling "
"conventions. See the section on [calling conventions](#calling-"
"conventions) for more information on this subject."
msgstr ""
"对于非标准x86调用协定, Koffi会自动尝试修饰名称. 参见[调用协定]节以获取更多该方面的信息."

#: ../../functions.md:44
msgid ""
"If you prefer, you can declare functions using simple C-like prototype "
"strings, as shown below:"
msgstr ""
"如果你喜欢, 你也可以使用简单的C风格原型字符串来声明函数, 如下所示:"

#: ../../functions.md:51
msgid "You can use `()` or `(void)` for functions that take no argument."
msgstr "对于不接受参数的函数, 你可以使用`()`或`(void)`."

#: ../../functions.md:53
msgid "Variadic functions"
msgstr "可变参数函数"

#: ../../functions.md:55
msgid "Variadic functions are declared with an ellipsis as the last argument."
msgstr "通过将省略号作为最后一个参数来声明可变参数函数"

#: ../../functions.md:57
msgid ""
"In order to call a variadic function, you must provide two Javascript "
"arguments for each additional C parameter, the first one is the expected "
"type and the second one is the value."
msgstr ""
"要调用一个可变参数函数, 你必须为每个额外的C参数提供两个Javascript参数, 前者是预期的类型, 后者是值."

#: ../../functions.md:66
msgid ""
"On x86 platforms, only the Cdecl convention can be used for variadic "
"functions."
msgstr ""
"对于x86平台, 只有Cdecl调用协定支持变长参数函数."

#: ../../functions.md:68
msgid "Calling conventions"
msgstr "调用协定"

#: ../../functions.md:70
msgid "By default, calling a C function happens synchronously."
msgstr "默认情况下, 调用一个C函数是同步的."

#: ../../functions.md:72
msgid ""
"Most architectures only support one procedure call standard per process. "
"The 32-bit x86 platform is an exception to this, and Koffi supports "
"several x86 conventions:"
msgstr ""
"大部分架构对于每个进程仅支持一种函数调用标准. "
"32位x86平台是一个例外, 且Koffi支持若干种x86调用协定:"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "Convention"
msgstr "调用协定"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "Classic form"
msgstr "经典风格"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "Prototype form"
msgstr "原型风格"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "Description"
msgstr "描述"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "**Cdecl**"
msgstr "**Cdecl**"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "`koffi.cdecl` or `koffi.func`"
msgstr "`koffi.cdecl`或`koffi.func`"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "_(default)_"
msgstr "_(默认)_"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "This is the default convention, and the only one on other platforms"
msgstr "这是默认的调用协定, 以及其它平台上唯一的一种."

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "**Stdcall**"
msgstr "**Stdcall**"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "`koffi.stdcall`"
msgstr "`koffi.stdcall`"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "__stdcall"
msgstr "__stdcall"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "This convention is used extensively within the Win32 API"
msgstr "这个调用协定在Win32 API中广泛使用"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "**Fastcall**"
msgstr "**Fastcall**"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "`koffi.fastcall`"
msgstr "`koffi.fastcall`"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "__fastcall"
msgstr "__fastcall"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "Rarely used, uses ECX and EDX for first two parameters"
msgstr "很少使用, 将前两个参数存入ECX和EDX"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "**Thiscall**"
msgstr "**Thiscall**"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "`koffi.thiscall`"
msgstr "`koffi.thiscall`"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "__thiscall"
msgstr "__thiscall"

#: ../../functions.md:18
msgid "Rarely used, uses ECX for first parameter"
msgstr "很少使用, 将第一个参数存入ECX"

#: ../../functions.md:81
msgid "You can safely use these on non-x86 platforms, they are simply ignored."
msgstr "你可以安全的在非x86平台中使用这些, 它们会被忽略."

#: ../../functions.md:83
msgid ""
"Below you can find a small example showing how to use a non-default "
"calling convention, with the two syntaxes:"
msgstr ""
"下面你可以看到一个简单的例子, 展示了两种语法下如何使用非默认的调用协定:"

#: ../../functions.md:96
msgid "Call types"
msgstr "调用类型"

#: ../../functions.md:98
msgid "Synchronous calls"
msgstr "同步调用"

#: ../../functions.md:100
msgid ""
"Once a native function has been declared, you can simply call it as you "
"would any other JS function."
msgstr ""
"当一个原生函数被声明, 你可以简单地像其它JS函数一样调用它."

#: ../../functions.md:109
msgid ""
"For [variadic functions](functions.md#variadic-functions), you msut "
"specificy the type and the value for each additional argument."
msgstr ""
"对于[可变参数函数](functions.md#variadic-functions), 你必须为每个额外的参数提供类型和值."

#: ../../functions.md:118
msgid "Asynchronous calls"
msgstr "异步调用"

#: ../../functions.md:120
msgid ""
"You can issue asynchronous calls by calling the function through its "
"async member. In this case, you need to provide a callback function as "
"the last argument, with `(err, res)` parameters."
msgstr "你可以通过调用函数的async成员来发起异步调用. 这种情况下, 你需要提供一个回调函数作为最后一个参数, 参数为`(err, res)`."

#: ../../functions.md:140
msgid ""
"These calls are executed by worker threads. It is **your responsibility "
"to deal with data sharing issues** in the native code that may be caused "
"by multi-threading."
msgstr ""
"这些调用会在worker线程中执行. 你**有责任处理**原生代码中可能由多线程引起的数据共享问题。"

#: ../../functions.md:142
msgid ""
"You can easily convert this callback-style async function to a promise-"
"based version with `util.promisify()` from the Node.js standard library."
msgstr ""
"你可以简单的通过Node.js标准库中的`util.promisify()`来将这个回调风格的一部函数转换为promise风格."

#: ../../functions.md:144
msgid "Variadic functions cannot be called asynchronously."
msgstr "可变参数函数不能被异步调用."

#: ../../functions.md:147
msgid ""
"Asynchronous functions run on worker threads. You need to deal with "
"thread safety issues if you share data between threads."
msgstr ""
"异步函数在worker线程中执行. 如果你在线程中共享数据, 你需要解决引发的线程安全问题."

#: ../../functions.md:149
msgid ""
"Callbacks must be called from the main thread, or more precisely from the"
" same thread as the V8 intepreter. Calling a callback from another thread"
" is undefined behavior, and will likely lead to a crash or a big mess. "
"You've been warned!"
msgstr ""
"回调必须在主线程中被调用, 准确来讲和V8解释器同一个线程. 从另一个线程中调用回调是未定义行为, "
"并且大概率会导致程序崩溃或混乱. 你已经被警告了!"

#: ../../functions.md:152
msgid "Function pointers"
msgstr "函数指针"

#: ../../functions.md:154
msgid "*New in Koffi 2.4*"
msgstr "*Koffi 2.4引入*"

#: ../../functions.md:156
msgid "You can call a function pointer in two ways:"
msgstr "你可以通过两种方式调用一个函数指针:"

#: ../../functions.md:158
msgid "Directly call the function pointer with `koffi.call(ptr, type, ...)`"
msgstr "通过`koffi.call(ptr, type, ...)`直接调用一个函数指针"

#: ../../functions.md:159
msgid ""
"Decode the function pointer to an actual function with `koffi.decode(ptr,"
" type)`"
msgstr ""
"通过`koffi.decode(ptr, type)`将函数指针解码成一个实际的函数"

#: ../../functions.md:161
msgid ""
"The example below shows how to call an `int (*)(int, int)` C function "
"pointer both ways, based on the following native C library:"
msgstr ""
"下面的例子展示了如何用两种方式调用一个`int (*)(int, int)`C函数, 基于下面的原生C库:"

#: ../../functions.md:181
msgid "Call pointer directly"
msgstr "直接调用指针"

#: ../../functions.md:183
msgid ""
"Use `koffi.call(ptr, type, ...)` to call a function pointer. The first "
"two arguments are the pointer itself and the type of the function you are"
" trying to call (declared with `koffi.proto()` as shown below), and the "
"remaining arguments are used for the call."
msgstr ""
"使用`koffi.call(ptr, type, ...)`来调用一个函数指针. 前两个参数是函数指针和函数的类型"
"(如下所示, 通过`koffi.proto()`定义), 其它参数则被用于调用本身."

#: ../../functions.md:200
msgid "Decode pointer to function"
msgstr "解码指针为函数"

#: ../../functions.md:202
msgid ""
"Use `koffi.decode(ptr, type)` to get back a JS function, which you can "
"then use like any other Koffi function."
msgstr ""
"使用`koffi.decode(ptr, type)`来获得一个JS函数, 你可以像其他Koffi函数一样使用它."

#: ../../functions.md:204
msgid ""
"This method also allows you to perform an [asynchronous call"
"](#asynchronous-calls) with the async member of the decoded function."
msgstr ""
"这个方法也允许你通过解码得到的函数的async成员来发起一个[异步调用](#asynchronous-calls)."

#: ../../functions.md:221
msgid "Conversion of parameters"
msgstr "参数转换"

#: ../../functions.md:223
msgid ""
"By default, Koffi will only forward and translate arguments from "
"Javascript to C. However, many C functions use pointer arguments for "
"output values, or input/output values."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下, Koffi只会从Javascript向C转发并翻译参数. 然而, 许多C函数使用指针参数来输出值, 或同时输入输出值."

